# --- POA private blockchain server configurations

Private blockchain configured using Proof of Authority
104.211.1.154:8081 to see a status of the blocks

We have two sealer nodes doing the validation/mining a bootnode and a ethstats configured as follows:

platform.genetank.ai: did not add any nodes because everyone seems to be using it
platform2.genetank.ai: used puppeth to configure platform3.genetank.ai and platform4.genetank.ai
platform3.genetank.ai: has sealer node + bootnode + ethstats
platform4.genetank.ai: has sealer node only

Other userful document:
